- **GRAPH**: "Likely has Document node" → "Ensure edges to Privacy Barriers, The Herd Protocol, Security Scanner. LLM Content Boundaries and Tiered Visibility should be Concept nodes." (Privacy concepts deserve their own graph presence.)

