### Enrichment
The 2026 International AI Safety Report emphasizes defense-in-depth for AI risk management. Anthropic abandoned opt-in for training data as of Sep 2025 — all providers now train on inputs by default, validating the need for local content filtering. RECAP framework combines regex with context-aware LLMs for PII detection. California Training Data Transparency Act (AB2013) takes effect 2026. The filter_for_llm approach aligns with industry best practices for data minimization.

